init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day, the news was all about the rankings.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day, all of the "#1 Mom" mugs changed to show the actual ranking of Moms.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next day, all of the "#1 Grandpa" mugs changed to show the actual ranking of Grandpas.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They were being their best selves, in the shadows.
